The Minority Ethnic Talent Assn (META) programme 'Growing Talent' is a Government Talent programme for black & minority ethnic (BAME) employees at Grade 6 /7 level to develop leadership skills. The programme supports participants to realise their ambition & potential to become future senior leaders in the Civil Service (CS). As a department we are committed to supporting this programme & improving our representation of BAME staff at SCS. Addressing under-representation in senior grades across government is a  key part of the CS Talent Action Plan.
